dataJson.name: Meet at mine
dataJson.story: Android project I build together with Yusuf, Radu and Kristian for the VIA Semester project. The requirement was to build a social app, we came up with the idea to build an app to organize meetings at someone's house, so we named it Meet at mine. Not much was learned from this project, since it looked so much like the Android project we did, but it was an interesting experience non the less
